{"baseRefName":"main","body":"## Commit Contents:\r\n- Added test to ensure there are no string literals\r\n- Added test to ensure a string is translated in all language files\r\n- Added missing strings in properties\r\n- Internationalized remaining strings flagged by the tests\r\n\r\n## Context:\r\n- This makes it easier to enforce that we always follow internationalization, and a preventive approach works better than searching and fixing individual strings later.\r\n- This test flagged each missing string for me, and I was able to resolve each one of them.\r\n","comments":[{"id":"IC_kwDOAHK23s6p8pPo","author":{"login":"anizmo"},"authorAssociation":"CONTRIBUTOR","body":"Could someone please assist me in merging this? This one is approved, but I don't see an option to merge it.\r\nFYI @dsyer ","createdAt":"2025-05-05T14:45:42Z","includesCreatedEdit":true,"isMinimized":false,"minimizedReason":"","reactionGroups":[],"url":"https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-petclinic/pull/1878#issuecomment-2851247080","viewerDidAuthor":false}],"files":[{"path":"src/main/resources/messages/messages.properties","additions":15,"deletions":0},{"path":"src/main/resources/messages/messages_de.properties","additions":15,"deletions":0},{"path":"src/main/resources/messages/messages_es.properties","additions":15,"deletions":0},{"path":"src/main/resources/messages/messages_fa.properties","additions":15,"deletions":0},{"path":"src/main/resources/messages/messages_ko.properties","additions":15,"deletions":0},{"path":"src/main/resources/messages/messages_pt.properties","additions":15,"deletions":0},{"path":"src/main/resources/messages/messages_ru.properties","additions":15,"deletions":0},{"path":"src/main/resources/messages/messages_tr.properties","additions":15,"deletions":0},{"path":"src/main/resources/templates/fragments/inputField.html","additions":2,"deletions":2},{"path":"src/main/resources/templates/fragments/layout.html","additions":3,"deletions":2},{"path":"src/main/resources/templa